000001 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
000002 PROGRAM-ID. TEST.
000003*This is a test program demonstrating COBOL operations
000004 DATA DIVISION.
000005*Variable declarations
000006 01 NAME PICTURE IS A(10).
000007 01 SUMMATION PICTURE IS 9.
000008 01 RESULT PICTURE IS 9.
000009*Main procedure section
000010 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
000011*Display greeting messages
000012 DISPLAY "HELLO
000013- WORLD".
000014 DISPLAY "Goede
000015- morgen".
000016 DISPLAY "".
000016 DISPLAY "12345".
000017 DISPLAY "NAME:" NAME.
000018*Prompt user for input
000019 DISPLAY "Enter value:"
000020- WITH NO ADVANCING.
000021 ACCEPT NAME.
000022*Arithmetic operations
000023 ADD 1 2 TO SUMMATION.
000024
000025 DIVIDE 1 INTO 2 GIVING RESULT.
000026
000027*Multiplication operations
000028 MULTIPLY 2 BY SUMMATION.
000029 MULTIPLY 3 BY SUMMATION GIVING RESULT.
000030 MULTIPLY 2 BY SUMMATION RESULT.
